name: particleboard production, cement bonded | particleboard, cement bonded | Cutoff, S
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/1892/documentation

This dataset presents particle board production, cement bonded.

From cradle, i.e. including all upstream activities.

Includes the inputs to the production processes. No process emission data are available.
